[I] Interactive Geometry

[T] Kig is an interactive mathematics software for learning and teaching
[T] geometry. It allows to explore mathematical figures and concepts using the
[T] computer and also can serve as a drawing tool for mathematical figures.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kig/

